      "updated": 1771918248026,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ONLY package importable from ALL layers\nTypes and enums ONLY — no logic\n\nState Machine:\n  MasteryState, ReviewGrade, ReviewModality\n  ItemType, LearningModality, ContextType\n\nFSRS:\n  FsrsState { due, stability, difficulty, ... }\n\nIPC (desktop):\n  IPC_CHANNELS (50+ method constants)\n  IpcChannel (union type)\n\nAuth & Onboarding:\n  AuthUser { id, email, name, avatarUrl,\n             onboardingCompleted }\n  SelfReportedLevel, OnboardingResult\n  AssessmentItem\n\nPayloads:\n  ReviewSubmission, ReviewQueueItem\n  ConversationMessage, SessionPlan\n  PostSessionAnalysis, ExpandedTomBrief\n  KnowledgeBubble, CurriculumRecommendation",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ONLY package importable from ALL layers\nTypes and enums ONLY — no logic\n\nState Machine:\n  MasteryState, ReviewGrade, ReviewModality\n  ItemType, LearningModality, ContextType\n\nFSRS:\n  FsrsState { due, stability, difficulty, ... }\n\nIPC (desktop):\n  IPC_CHANNELS (50+ method constants)\n  IpcChannel (union type)\n\nAuth & Onboarding:\n  AuthUser { id, email, name, avatarUrl,\n             onboardingCompleted }\n  SelfReportedLevel, OnboardingResult\n  AssessmentItem\n\nPayloads:\n  ReviewSubmission, ReviewQueueItem\n  ConversationMessage, SessionPlan\n  PostSessionAnalysis, ExpandedTomBrief\n  KnowledgeBubble, CurriculumRecommendation",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
