    {
      "id": "elem_375_5c4015b3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 72,
      "y": 6613,
      "width": 294.52,
      "height": 267.25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "elem_371_1c20b9bd"
      ],
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771918248027,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. apps/ NEVER import from each other\n   (desktop and web are independent)\n\n2. @linguist/core has ZERO deps on\n   Electron, React, Next.js, or Prisma\n   (pure functions only)\n\n3. Only IPC handlers (desktop) and\n   API routes (web) touch @linguist/db\n\n4. @linguist/shared is the ONLY\n   package importable everywhere\n\n5. All DB queries scoped by userId\n   (no data leakage between users)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. apps/ NEVER import from each other\n   (desktop and web are independent)\n\n2. @linguist/core has ZERO deps on\n   Electron, React, Next.js, or Prisma\n   (pure functions only)\n\n3. Only IPC handlers (desktop) and\n   API routes (web) touch @linguist/db\n\n4. @linguist/shared is the ONLY\n   package importable everywhere\n\n5. All DB queries scoped by userId\n   (no data leakage between users)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
