      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Completed (this update):\n  [x] Supabase Auth (Google OAuth)\n  [x] Monorepo migration (Turborepo)\n  [x] Next.js web app (feature parity)\n  [x] Onboarding / placement wizard\n\nNext priorities:\n  [ ] @linguist/ui shared component pkg\n  [ ] Word bank detail view + editing\n  [ ] Error handling UX (toasts, boundaries)\n  [ ] Session summary enrichment\n  [ ] Chat integration w/ knowledge model\n  [ ] Insights page (ToM display)\n  [ ] Testing (core/ + API routes)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Completed (this update):\n  [x] Supabase Auth (Google OAuth)\n  [x] Monorepo migration (Turborepo)\n  [x] Next.js web app (feature parity)\n  [x] Onboarding / placement wizard\n\nNext priorities:\n  [ ] @linguist/ui shared component pkg\n  [ ] Word bank detail view + editing\n  [ ] Error handling UX (toasts, boundaries)\n  [ ] Session summary enrichment\n  [ ] Chat integration w/ knowledge model\n  [ ] Insights page (ToM display)\n  [ ] Testing (core/ + API routes)",
